                        - Choose the appropriate week from the Select Week dropdown. This will populate the table with the days of the selected week.
                   
                        2. Fill in the Time Report:
                        - Day and Date: The table will display the days and dates of the selected week.
                        - Start Time: Enter the start time for each day in the Start Time column.
                        - End Time: Enter the end time for each day in the End Time column.
                        - Lunch Start: Enter the start time of your lunch break in the Lunch Start column.
                        - Lunch End: Enter the end time of your lunch break in the Lunch End column.
                        - Working Hours: This field will show the calculated working hours for each day.
                        - Total Working Hours (Alternate Option): If you choose to use the alternative option, enter the total working hours directly.
                        - FlexiTime: Enter any flexitime hours for each day.
                        - Overtime: Enter any overtime hours for each day.
                        - MoreTime: Enter any additional hours if applicable.

                        3. Alternative Option:
                        - If you prefer to use an alternative method for filling the form, click the choose alternative option to fill button.
                        - This will toggle the enable/disable state of the input fields for Start Time, End Time, Lunch Start, and Lunch End.
                        - When enabled, you can enter the times manually.
                        - When disabled, the form will set Working Hours to 8 and Total Working Hours to 0 automatically. You can then adjust these fields as needed.

                        4. Submit the Form:
                        - Once all the fields are filled out, click the Submit button at the bottom of the form to submit your time report.

                        Summary of Fields and Actions:
                        - Select Week: Choose the desired week from the dropdown.
                        - Start Time: Enter the time you started work each day.
                        - End Time: Enter the time you finished work each day.
                        - Lunch Start: Enter the start time of your lunch break each day.
                        - Lunch End: Enter the end time of your lunch break each day.
                        - Working Hours: This field is calculated based on your start and end times.
                        - Total Working Hours (Alternate Option): Directly enter the total working hours for the day.
                        - FlexiTime: Enter any flexitime hours.
                        - Overtime: Enter any overtime hours.
                        - MoreTime: Enter any additional hours.

                        Additional Notes:
                        - Validation: If there are any validation errors, they will be highlighted in red and must be corrected before submission.
                        - API Integration: The form fetches public holiday data to highlight red days (holidays). These days will be displayed in red text.

